author: Ali Vitali, Ben Kamisar
title: Elizabeth Warren endorses Joe Biden
description: Warren announced her decision in a message on Twitter, where she said that America needs an empathetic president like Biden to help Americans reconnect with the federal government.
content:
Elizabeth Warren endorses Joe Biden
WASHINGTON Sen. Elizabeth Warren endorsed former Vice President Joe Biden's presidential bid Wednesday, making her the latest prominent Democrat to publicly throw their support behind Biden in recent days.
